# PDF Metadata Extractor
A simple command-line tool to extract and display metadata from PDF files using the UniDoc/UniPDF library.

# Description
This tool allows you to quickly extract and view metadata information from PDF files, including:

- Title
- Author
- Subject
- Creator

# Usage
## Options
--help or -h: Show help message and usage examples
## Examples
./pdfinfo document.pdf
./pdfinfo "C:\Documents\report.pdf"
./pdfinfo /home/user/files/presentation.pdf
